title: Nourish
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Fast food, Take-out, British, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Healthier fast food cafe in central Leeds. Menu changes from time to time and is labeled with a range of dietary requirements listed including vegan, vegetarian, gluten-free, nut and wheat allergies. Breakfast options such as porridge; falafel and hummus; salad; baked sweet potato with your choice of topping; pumpkin and vegetable masala curry; vegan chilli and rice; a couple of wraps.
